name: Attributes_sizeTest
description: Unit tests for the size functionality of the Attributes class.

test_cases.name: testSizeEmpty
test_cases.description: Tests the size of an empty Attributes object.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterAdd
test_cases.description: Tests the size of the Attributes object after adding an attribute.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterRemove
test_cases.description: Tests the size of the Attributes object after adding and then removing an attribute.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterAddAll
test_cases.description: Tests the size of the Attributes object after adding multiple attributes using addAll.
